sentences: Ma olen tegelenud sellega juba mitu aastat.
Ta on tegelenud muusikaga alates lapsepõlvest.
Nad on tegelenud selle küsimusega juba kaua.
context: The word 'tegelenud' is the past participle form of the Estonian verb 'tegelema', which means to deal with or cope with something, and it is commonly used in sentences to describe a person's experience or involvement with an activity or situation.
